== comment.end-of-line-comment == append ==
# <CURSOR>
§%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
== comment.frame ==
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  <CURSOR>
#---------------------------------------------------------------------------
§%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
== comment.function ==
#===  FUNCTION  ================================================================
#         NAME:  |?FUNCTION_NAME|
#      PURPOSE:  <CURSOR>
#   PARAMETERS:  ????
#      RETURNS:  ????
#  DESCRIPTION:  ????
#       THROWS:  no exceptions
#     COMMENTS:  none
#     SEE ALSO:  n/a
#===============================================================================
§%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
== comment.method ==
#===  CLASS METHOD  ============================================================
#        CLASS:  |?CLASSNAME|
#       METHOD:  |?METHODNAME|
#   PARAMETERS:  ????
#      RETURNS:  ????
#  DESCRIPTION:  <CURSOR>
#       THROWS:  no exceptions
#     COMMENTS:  none
#     SEE ALSO:  n/a
#===============================================================================
